{"results":[{"aya":"050","id":4464,"locale":"zh","sura":"044","text":"这（刑罚）确是你们生前所怀疑的。","translator":"Ma Jian"},{"aya":"051","id":4465,"locale":"zh","sura":"044","text":"敬畏者必定要住在安全的地方--","translator":"Ma Jian"},{"aya":"052","id":4466,"locale":"zh","sura":"044","text":"住在乐园之中，住在泉源之滨，","translator":"Ma Jian"},{"aya":"053","id":4467,"locale":"zh","sura":"044","text":"穿着绫罗绸缎，相向而坐。","translator":"Ma Jian"},{"aya":"054","id":4468,"locale":"zh","sura":"044","text":"结局是这样的：我将以白皙的、美目的女子，做他们的伴侣。","translator":"Ma Jian"},{"aya":"055","id":4469,"locale":"zh","sura":"044","text":"他们在乐园中，将安全地索取各种水果。","translator":"Ma Jian"},{"aya":"056","id":4470,"locale":"zh","sura":"044","text":"他们在乐园中，除初次死亡外不再尝死的滋味。真主将使他们得免于火狱的刑罚。","translator":"Ma Jian"}],"metadata":{"itemsPerPage":7,"pages":9,"previousPage":"/zh/s044-7.json","nextPage":"/zh/s044-9.json"}}